        <h1 class="xl black">3. Win:<span class="blue">Win</span></h1>
        <p class="larger blue">
          One of the most important skills of being an innovator is ensuring that you create a win:win situation.
        </p>
        <div class="list">
          <h5>You are driving along in your car on a wild, stormy night. You pass by a bus stop, and you see three people waiting for the bus: </h5>
          <ul>
            <li><p>An old lady who looks as if she is about to die. </p>
            </li>
            <li><p>An old friend who once saved your life. </p>
            </li>
            <li><p>The perfect man (or) woman you have been dreaming about.</p>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <p><b>There is only room for one passenger in your car. What do you do?</b> You could pick up the old lady, because she is going to die, and thus you should save her first; or you could take the old friend because he once saved your life, and this would be the perfect chance to pay him back. However, you may never be able to find your perfect dream lover again.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="row panel video">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
