        <div class="reveal">
         <ul id="accord3" class="accordian">
           <li>
             <header>
               <div class="row">
                 <div class="col-sm-11 col-xs-12">
                    <h1>Creating a win:win </h1>
                 </div>
                 <div class="col-sm-1 hidden-xs">
                     <i class="fa fa-chevron-down hidden-xs" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                 </div>
               </div>
             </header>
             <section>
                <p>Create a win:win for everyone and your idea and business will grow faster and be more successful. The long term success of a business means creating a situation where all involved gain and win in the operation of the business.
                </p>
                <div class="list">
                  <p><b>Before you go to any meeting, with a teacher, supervisor, colleague, think:</b></p>
                  <ul>
                    <li><p>“What do I want to gain from this meeting?”</p>
                    </li>
                    <li><p>“What things might the other person want to gain?”</p>
                    </li>
                    <li><p>“How can I help him/her get what they want, so that I can get what I want, so that we both achieve win:win?”</p>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
